    Heat Guardian is a hardcore top-down shooter set in a freezing        
    world. You'll have to travel through the dying lands to find the      
    one last stronghold of humanity û trying your best to stay            
    alive. Deadly mutants, limited resources and even the world           
    itself make this journey a trial only the most skilled survivors      
    can endure.                                                           
                                                                          
    NOTES: This release is standalone and updated to current version.     
                                                                          
